item.title: Marcus Thompson
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Head Coach Marcus Thompson brings over 20 years of elite coaching experience to Florida Coastal Prep. Former Division I standout and professional player, Coach Thompson specializes in player development and tactical strategy.
